name: Not To Be Reproduced ReImagined (from the Magritte Reimagined collection)
description: This is a collection that takes the work of surrealist Rene Magritte and reimagines it as photographs. The subjects are replaced with people of color and the inanimate objects are replaced with classic cameras. This piece was the most difficult one for me to create. I hope you like it. The model is one of my best friends.
